(1652, 177, '_about_header', 'field_595fe87d29082'),
(1653, 177, 'profile_picture', '123'),
(1654, 177, '_profile_picture', 'field_595fed0dbc52a'),
(1655, 177, 'experience_0_experience-title', 'Web Developer @ Foundry Digital'),
(1656, 177, '_experience_0_experience-title', 'field_595ffb5019b91'),
(1657, 177, 'experience_0_experience-duration', 'March 2015 - Present'),
(1658, 177, '_experience_0_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(1659, 177, 'experience_0_experience-text', 'I am having absolute pleasure to meet these guys and be part of the team since 2015.\r\nIn Foundry digital, I am responsible for the development of the projects, Front and Back end as well as the back-end SEO maintenance.'),
(1660, 177, '_experience_0_experience-text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
(1661, 177, 'experience_0_position', 'right'),
(1662, 177, '_experience_0_position', 'field_595ffbaa28515'),
(1663, 177, 'experience_1_experience-title', 'Graphic Designer @ Gradeline'),
(1664, 177, '_experience_1_experience-title', 'field_595ffb5019b91'),
(1665, 177, 'experience_1_experience-duration', 'Nov 2009 - Aug 2014'),
(1666, 177, '_experience_1_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(1667, 177, 'experience_1_experience-text', 'Since the age of 17, I have been working as a graphic designer, part-time and full-time and I have being earning my own salaries since then (which teach me a lot of life lessons).\r\nThe job required to work under pressure, to have a very good time-management and to be self-organised. It mostly has taught me to meet deadlines on time, work in a team, efficiency and make quick decisions in crisis.'),
(1668, 177, '_experience_1_experience-text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
(1669, 177, 'experience_1_position', 'left'),
(1670, 177, '_experience_1_position', 'field_595ffbaa28515'),
(1671, 177, 'experience', '6'),
(1672, 177, '_experience', 'field_595ffb4319b90'),
(1673, 177, 'experience_2_experience-title', 'Web Developer Course - ONLINE'),
(1674, 177, '_experience_2_experience-title', 'field_595ffb5019b91'),
(1675, 177, 'experience_2_experience-duration', 'Aug 2014 - Dec 2014'),
(1676, 177, '_experience_2_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(1677, 177, 'experience_2_experience-text', 'After graduating with a Computer Science degree, I decided to keep my habit of studing and do a course over Web development. It was a good experience finding out new ways of achieving certain tasks and watching profesionals executing them. I was asked to build web pages by using HTML &amp; CSS with JQuery animation and effects. I would rate this course as a very good practice.'),
(1678, 177, '_experience_2_experience-text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
(1679, 177, 'experience_2_position', 'right'),
(1680, 177, '_experience_2_position', 'field_595ffbaa28515'),
(1681, 177, 'experience_3_experience-title', 'Skill Boost & Leadership Programme'),
(1682, 177, '_experience_3_experience-title', 'field_595ffb5019b91'),
(1683, 177, 'experience_3_experience-duration', 'Aug 2014 - Dec 2014'),
(1684, 177, '_experience_3_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(1685, 177, 'experience_3_experience-text', 'Skill Boost Programme and Leadership Programme are two different courses which were offered to me after I have graduated. Skill Boost was aiming at teaching basic skills from finding a job to keep it and do well at it.\r\nLeadership Programme was more about getting involved in the project and becoming a teamleader. Luckily, I am very flexible and self-improving person and knowing how to be helpful and being useful motivates me a lot, these courses personally helped me improve my emotional intelligence and find the better approach to my job and the people I work with.'),
(1686, 177, '_experience_3_experience-text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
(1687, 177, 'experience_3_position', 'left'),
(1688, 177, '_experience_3_position', 'field_595ffbaa28515'),
(1689, 177, 'experience_4_experience-title', 'Bachlor at Middlesex University'),
(1690, 177, '_experience_4_experience-title', 'field_595ffb5019b91'),
(1691, 177, 'experience_4_experience-duration', 'Graduated: 2014'),
(1692, 177, '_experience_4_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(1693, 177, 'experience_4_experience-text', 'I started my Bachlor degree in 2011, studying Bcs Computer Science. During my 3 years of studying a was instroduced to many different programming languages such as HTML, CSS, PHP, AJAX, JS, C++, JAVA, C, Visual Basic and many other side tasks to improve my creativity and knowledge. Shortly said, the university was one great kick-start in finding my life path.'),
(1694, 177, '_experience_4_experience-text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
(1695, 177, 'experience_4_position', 'right'),
(1696, 177, '_experience_4_position', 'field_595ffbaa28515'),
(1697, 177, 'experience_5_experience-title', 'BTEC NC'),
(1698, 177, '_experience_5_experience-title', 'field_595ffb5019b91'),
(1699, 177, 'experience_5_experience-duration', 'Sept 2009 - May 2011'),
(1700, 177, '_experience_5_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(1701, 177, 'experience_5_experience-text', 'Right after I started practicing development as a hobby, I decided to continue my education the same sphere. Studying 2 years of IT was very useful before going to university, because was where I dived more than just the basic and I gained new knowledge and confidence in the area.\r\nThe most I was asked to work on In college was HTML, CSS and Photoshop.'),
(1702, 177, '_experience_5_experience-text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
(1703, 177, 'experience_5_position', 'left'),
(1704, 177, '_experience_5_position', 'field_595ffbaa28515'),
(1705, 177, 'experience_text', 'In my free time you can catch me putting together different bits of code and constructing some fancy functions. I enjoy building my own WordPress responsive themes and spend time on improving my knowledge and skills. I love my job, as it is my hobby too, and this makes it very pleasant for me. I am very open to new challenges, please have a look at some of my projects and do not hesitate to contact me so we can discuss your ideas. Read my story so you can get to know me better!'),
(1706, 177, '_experience_text', 'field_596008dbec68d'),
