(2098, 238, '_experience_2_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(2099, 238, 'experience_2_experience-text', 'After graduating with a Computer Science degree, I decided to keep my habit of studing and do a course over Web development. It was a good experience finding out new ways of achieving certain tasks and watching profesionals executing them. I was asked to build web pages by using HTML &amp; CSS with JQuery animation and effects. I would rate this course as a very good practice.'),
