(2114, 238, '_experience_4_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(2115, 238, 'experience_4_experience-text', 'I started my Bachlor degree in 2011, studying Bcs Computer Science. During my 3 years of studying a was instroduced to many different programming languages such as HTML, CSS, PHP, AJAX, JS, C++, JAVA, C, Visual Basic and many other side tasks to improve my creativity and knowledge. Shortly said, the university was one great kick-start in finding my life path.'),
