(3556, 415, 'experience_1_experience-text', 'Since the age of 17, I have been working as a graphic designer, part-time and full-time and I have being earning my own salaries since then (which teach me a lot of life lessons).\r\nThe job required to work under pressure, to have a very good time-management and to be self-organised. It mostly has taught me to meet deadlines on time, work in a team, efficiency and make quick decisions in crisis.'),
