(3877, 422, '_experience_1_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(3878, 422, 'experience_1_experience-text', 'Started working part-time as a graphic designer whilst in college. My duties included transfering clothes patterns from paper to computer and then correcting and aligning all pieces together as a single graphic. This job has perfected my attention to detail as well as working under pressure in order to meet deadlines. This often required multitasking and being very creative. It also increased my interest in graphic design and I started exploring it further in my classes at college.'),
