(3887, 422, '_experience_2_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(3888, 422, 'experience_2_experience-text', 'Web Developer Course - ONLINE Aug 2014 - Dec 2014 After graduating with a Computer Science degree, I decided to keep my habit of studing and do a course over Web development.I completed a short online course as a part of my continuing professional development which showed me how ro easily find new ways of achieving different web development tasks. I had the chance to watch profesionals execute different coding ........ and asked to build web pages by utilising the newly learned skills. I gained more creative skills using HTML and CSS with JQuery animation and effects.'),
