(5422, 8, '_experience_6_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(5423, 8, 'experience_6_experience-text', 'During my degree I was instroduced to even more programmig languages including Wordpress API, JQuery, PHP , My SQL, C++ and JAVA. I broadened my knowledge and horizons even more and after three years of dedication I was absolutely sure web development will become my future successful career!\r\n\r\nModules Included: Database, Management Systems, Introduction to Operating Systems,\r\nArchitecture and Networks, Discovering Interaction Design, Programming with Data\r\nStructures and Algorithms, Object Oriented Analysis and Design, Professional Project\r\nDevelopment and Management, Object Oriented Software Development, Introduction\r\nto Computer Graphics, Client/Server Web System Development, Distributed and Mobile\r\nGames, Software Development Project, Current Topics in Computer Science.'),
(5424, 8, '_experience_6_experience-text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
