(5430, 8, '_experience_7_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(5431, 8, 'experience_7_experience-text', 'After discovering and practicing web development as a hobby, I continued my education in that area in college. I studied IT for two years and I managed to expand my knowledge and skills beyond basics. This experience consolidated my decision to continue pursuing it further.\r\n\r\nI gained a solid understanding of multiple subjects ranging from Cisco networking to HTML, CSS, Java Script and Adobe package (including Photoshop and Dreamweaver).'),
