(5475, 484, 'experience_4_experience-duration', 'Aug 2014 - Dec 2014'),
(5476, 484, '_experience_4_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(5477, 484, 'experience_4_experience-text', 'Web Developer Course - ONLINE Aug 2014 - Dec 2014 After graduating with a Computer Science degree, I decided to keep my habit of studing and do a course over Web development.I completed a short online course as a part of my continuing professional development which showed me how ro easily find new ways of achieving different web development tasks. I had the chance to watch profesionals execute different coding ........ and asked to build web pages by utilising the newly learned skills. I gained more creative skills using HTML and CSS with JQuery animation and effects.'),
(5478, 484, '_experience_4_experience-text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
(5479, 484, 'experience_4_position', 'right'),
(5480, 484, '_experience_4_position', 'field_595ffbaa28515'),
(5481, 484, 'experience_5_experience-title', 'Skill Boost & Leadership Programme'),
(5482, 484, '_experience_5_experience-title', 'field_595ffb5019b91'),
(5483, 484, 'experience_5_experience-duration', 'Aug 2014 - Dec 2014'),
(5484, 484, '_experience_5_experience-duration', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(5485, 484, 'experience_5_experience-text', 'Skill Boost and Leadership are two separate courses which were offered to me as one programme after I have graduated from university. The Skill Boost Programme aimed at teaching basic skills from finding a job to keeping it and I acquired certain useful competencies which benefited me a lot when I was looking to start my career. The Leadership Programme was more about getting involved in projects and becoming a team leader. It helped me develop a better understanding of management and emotional intelligence as well as how to employ different approaches when working with people.'),
(5486, 484, '_experience_5_experience-text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
(5487, 484, 'experience_5_position', 'left'),
(5488, 484, '_experience_5_position', 'field_595ffbaa28515'),
(5489, 484, 'experience_text', 'In my free time, you can usually catch me putting together different bits of code or learning to construct new fancy functions. I enjoy building my own WordPress responsive themes and I spend quite a lot of time improving my knowledge and skills. I am open to challenges and ready to try and succeed!\r\n\r\nHave a read of my story so you can get to know me a lil bit better!'),
