(5759, 506, '_timeline_4_date', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(5760, 506, 'timeline_4_text', 'Web Developer Course – ONLINE Aug 2014 – Dec 2014 After graduating with a Computer Science degree, I decided to keep my habit of studing and do a course over Web development.I completed a short online course as a part of my continuing professional development which showed me how ro easily find new ways of achieving different web development tasks. I had the chance to watch profesionals execute different coding …….. and asked to build web pages by utilising the newly learned skills. I gained more creative skills using HTML and CSS with JQuery animation and effects.'),
(5761, 506, '_timeline_4_text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
(5762, 506, 'timeline_5_title', 'Skill Boost & Leadership Programme'),
(5763, 506, '_timeline_5_title', 'field_595ffb5019b91'),
(5764, 506, 'timeline_5_date', 'Aug 2014 - Dec 2014'),
(5765, 506, '_timeline_5_date', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(5766, 506, 'timeline_5_text', 'Skill Boost and Leadership are two separate courses which were offered to me as one programme after I have graduated from university. The Skill Boost Programme aimed at teaching basic skills from finding a job to keeping it and I acquired certain useful competencies which benefited me a lot when I was looking to start my career. The Leadership Programme was more about getting involved in projects and becoming a team leader. It helped me develop a better understanding of management and emotional intelligence as well as how to employ different approaches when working with people.'),
(5767, 506, '_timeline_5_text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
(5768, 506, 'timeline_6_title', 'Bachlor at Middlesex University'),
(5769, 506, '_timeline_6_title', 'field_595ffb5019b91'),
(5770, 506, 'timeline_6_date', 'Graduated: 2014'),
(5771, 506, '_timeline_6_date', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(5772, 506, 'timeline_6_text', 'During my degree I was instroduced to even more programmig languages including WordPress API, JQuery, PHP , My SQL, C++ and JAVA. I broadened my knowledge and horizons even more and after three years of dedication I was absolutely sure web development will become my future successful career!\r\n\r\nModules Included: Database, Management Systems, Introduction to Operating Systems,\r\nArchitecture and Networks, Discovering Interaction Design, Programming with Data\r\nStructures and Algorithms, Object Oriented Analysis and Design, Professional Project\r\nDevelopment and Management, Object Oriented Software Development, Introduction\r\nto Computer Graphics, Client/Server Web System Development, Distributed and Mobile\r\nGames, Software Development Project, Current Topics in Computer Science.'),
(5773, 506, '_timeline_6_text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
(5774, 506, 'timeline_7_title', 'BTEC NC'),
(5775, 506, '_timeline_7_title', 'field_595ffb5019b91'),
(5776, 506, 'timeline_7_date', 'Sept 2009 - May 2011'),
(5777, 506, '_timeline_7_date', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(5778, 506, 'timeline_7_text', 'After discovering and practicing web development as a hobby, I continued my education in that area in college. I studied IT for two years and I managed to expand my knowledge and skills beyond basics. This experience consolidated my decision to continue pursuing it further.\r\n\r\nI gained a solid understanding of multiple subjects ranging from Cisco networking to HTML, CSS, Java Script and Adobe package (including Photoshop and Dreamweaver).'),
(5779, 506, '_timeline_7_text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
