(6262, 520, 'timeline_0_date', 'March 2019 - Present'),
(6263, 520, '_timeline_0_date', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(6264, 520, 'timeline_0_text', 'In 2019 I started working at Global. My day to day work includes maintenance and developing new features on the radio brand sites and globalplayer.com, but I will save you the fluff and I will tell you the tech and tools we mostly use - React, NextJS, Webpack, React Testing Library, Jest, Docker, Django and many more.'),
(6265, 520, '_timeline_0_text', 'field_595ffb6c19b93'),
(6266, 520, 'timeline_1_title', 'Front-end developer @ Dusted'),
(6267, 520, '_timeline_1_title', 'field_595ffb5019b91'),
(6268, 520, 'timeline_1_date', 'August 2017 - March 2019'),
(6269, 520, '_timeline_1_date', 'field_595ffb5a19b92'),
(6270, 520, 'timeline_1_text', 'At Dusted I continued with my development of web products, most of which were websites on Wordpress and Drupal. As a comparison, the projects were a lot bigger in scale, the work was done for clients with a lot more traffic. I closely worked with the design team to make sure the final products meet the conditions of satisfaction. The tech stack was similar to the one in Foundry Digital, with the addition of tools such as Gulp, Grunt and a few different CSS frameworks.'),
