(6528, 523, 'experience_2_experience-text', 'In 2015 I joined the team at Foundry Digital as the main (and only) web developer. This is where I have been expanding and gaining the most know-how and skills working on big projects until recently, when I decided I am ready to progress further. At Foundry Digital I developed both front end and back end following a design created by the company\'s graphic designer. I competently used HTML, CSS, Java Script, JQuery, PHP and MySQL on Wordpress to create custom themes. I was also daily involved in the other aspects of building a website - meeting with clients and helping with graphic design. All that has helped me develop not only my expertise but also taught me to be patient and understanding in order to satisfy clients\' needs!'),
