(8, 1, '2017-06-29 20:52:12', '2017-06-29 19:52:12', 'Ivelin Iliev - Ivo\r\n\r\nLondon, United Kingdom\r\n\r\n+44 7828 124 770\r\n\r\nYes, I am one of those nerdy guys with big glasses, but more importantly - I am an enthusiastic web developer lucky to live in an ever-growing city of opportunities! With a passion for coding from a very young age, a Computer Science degree and a desire to advance and prosper, I help people by designing and developing functional yet aesthetic websites! I do not simply create websites but rather add the missing pieces to the puzzle - the puzzle that brings desired results, serves and entertains the end users and last but not least,  that makes me feel proud and accomplished! Helping others is part of my nature and I have found the way to do what I love by contributing to others\' success. This is why I accept every project personally and aim to make it best suit its purpose!', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2021-04-03 19:32:12', '2021-04-03 18:32:12', '', 0, 'http://localhost:8888/ivelin.me//?page_id=8', 0, 'page', '', 0),
