free to explore more of it from the<a href="https://git-scm.com/docs/git-bisect#_name"> git website</a>.\r\n\r\nIf you have any questions, feel free to message me, including If you\'d like to know where the index background image is from! Happy coding!', 'How to use git bisect', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '485-revision-v1', '', '', '2020-07-01 13:02:30', '2020-07-01 12:02:30', '', 485, 'https://localhost:8888/ivelin.me/485-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
